response.original_title: Garden State Pro Wrestling: Welcome To Eden
response.overview: On July 23rd Garden State Pro Wrestling debuts live with "Welcome To Eden" straight from The Heart Ballroom in Newark, New Jersey!  The event is double headlined by two huge main events. In both matches the contenders are stepping in the ring against each other for the first time ever - they are Josh Alexander vs Konosuke Takeshita and Taya Valkyrie vs Trish Adora.  The event features and the Openweight Championship 8 wrestler tournament. The first round matchups are already announced, check them below:  Davey Richards vs Robert Martyr, Kevin Blackwood vs Alan "5" Angels, Effy vs Bryan Keith & Tony Deppen vs Calvin Tankman. Other matches on the show include Miyu Yamashita vs Billie Starkz vs Janai Kai, Dark Sheik & Jai Vidal vs Edith Surreal & Heather Monroe and YDNB (Jordan Oliver, Charlie Tiger, Griffin McCoy) vs TEAM H20 (Marcus Mathers, Reid Walker, Austin Luke).
